content: I was depressed the whole time... but that’s fine, I guess.
I battled a carnivorous fish, but I bravely persevered and had a wonderful time.
Some of my  male coworkers tried to discourage me from visiting but I’m glad I didn’t listen. This was by far the best location for a planet I’ve ever been to, and I survived!
Very happy place. It’s a shame I’m never happy. Otherwise maybe I would have enjoyed it.
I nearly lost a leg to a neon pink unicorn with five heads, but I survived and had a great time!
